  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK881">
<l>niḻaṉīru miṉṉāta viṉṉā tamarnīru</l>
<l>miṉṉāvā miṉṉā ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Shade and water are not pleasant, (if) they cause disease; so are the qualities of (one's) relations not agreeable, (if) they cause pain.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
